.github/prompts/implement-feature.prompt.md
.github/prompts/scaffold-project.prompt.md
.github/skills/build/
.github/skills/test/
.github/skills/lint/
.github/skills/format/
.github/skills/deploy/

# .greenfield/ runtime data — project-specific, not part of the framework
